<recommendation type="Recommended" uid="14970">It is likely many viewers would write this off as just an anime for kids.  I was almost ready to do that with the first few episodes I saw.  I`m glad I stuck with it though, because it was one of the sweetest fantasy anime`s I`ve seen in a while.  Each mini arc of this show has a unique story and characters to go with it.  Beautiful and colorful animation style with stories of romance, adventure, quests and friendships.  With a lot of character interaction and some emotional depth, it seemed like it had somewhat of a slice of life feel to it.  For those who enjoy fantasy and adventure, I recommend you give this a try.  Perhaps you will find it as touching, playful, and beautiful as I did.</recommendation>
</recommendations>
